https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null Death Life Etc. is about homecoming…a homecoming made possible by a carnival in the traditional mountain society, some relationships, a few tales, stories and perhaps the film itself… A chronicle of the passage of seasons over scattered habitations tucked amidst Himalayan frontiers between Sikkim and Tibet, mapped by historic facts and fantastic tales. Death Life Etc.
